  "texts": [
    "The network primarily encounters confusion between the herbaceous vegetation class and the permanent crop class, as both categories share analogous appearance and morphological features.",
    "These outcomes highlight the RCA network's ability to harness clear spatial distinctions within high-resolution datasets, underscoring its effectiveness in scenarios where class features are visually distinct.",
    "However, the Eurosat dataset aligns well with the RCA network's strengths due to its highresolution imagery, distinct class boundaries, and a structured layout across the 10 categories.",
    "This dataset's lower inter-class similarity, especially among land-use classes such as built-up areas and forests, enables the RCA network to identify differentiating features with a high degree of accuracy.",
    "The experimental results, shown in Table 3 outlines the outcomes of our proposed method in contrast to four state-of-the-art approaches for remote sensing image scene classification, and demonstrates that our model achieved an overall classification accuracy of 96.3%, with most categories achieving over 95% accuracy."
